01:08:09,960 --> 01:08:13,546
The current Minister of Education
and head of the ERPB, Choi Gang-seok,

1039
01:08:13,547 --> 01:08:15,758
is the victim's father.

1040
01:08:17,176 --> 01:08:19,261
And Inspector Na Hwa-jin was her fiancé.

1041
01:08:29,230 --> 01:08:30,647
<i>Those investigated by the ERPB,</i>

1042
01:08:30,648 --> 01:08:34,275
<i>Ryu Jun-hyeong of Daehan High,
the students at Guun High-Tech High,</i>

1043
01:08:34,276 --> 01:08:37,780
<i>and Soyeon Girls' High School,
are all students.</i>

1044
01:08:39,490 --> 01:08:40,491
<i>Is it truly possible</i>

1045
01:08:41,200 --> 01:08:44,620
this has nothing to do with
the teacher killed by her student?

1046
01:08:45,204 --> 01:08:49,166
<i>These people are not working
for educational rights.</i>

1047
01:08:50,084 --> 01:08:51,460
<i>It is cruel revenge</i>

1048
01:08:52,586 --> 01:08:55,131
<i>for the death
of their daughter and fiancée.</i>

1049
01:08:57,758 --> 01:08:59,510
It is a personal vendetta.

1050
01:10:20,466 --> 01:10:23,427
Subtitle translation by: Lisa Kim
